s\">HasPullbacks</a></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_extends\">extends</span> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">P</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.Respects\">Respects</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.isomorphisms\">CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.isomorphisms</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span>)</span></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A property of morphisms `P` in `C` is local at the target with respect to the precoverage `K` if\nit respects isomorphisms, and:\n`P` holds for `f : X ⟶ Y` if and only if it holds for the restrictions of `f` to `Uᵢ` for a\n`0`-hypercover `{Uᵢ}` of `Y` in the precoverage `K`.\n\nFor a version of `of_zeroHypercover` that takes a `v`-small `0`-hypercover in an arbitrary\nuniverse, use `CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.of_zeroHypercover_target`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Local.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtTarget","kind":"class","line":49,"name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtTarget","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Local.lean#L49-L67"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Sites.Hypercover.Zero","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Limits.Shapes.Pullback.Equalizer","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.Limits"],"instances":[{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtTarget","name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtTarget.top","typeNames":["Top.top"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtTarget","name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtTarget.inf","typeNames":["Min.min"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtSource","name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtSource.top","typeNames":["Top.top"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtSource","name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtSource.inf","typeNames":["Min.min"]}],"name":"Mathlib.CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.Local"}